node.text:
🔸Dirty Bun SG @dirtybunsg 🔸// Burger is always better from @dirtybunsg 🍔. The patties are absolutely glorious, it’s smashed and griddled. Plus look at that a deep brown crust, that’s a thing of beauty. That takes my breath away.
And the flavour is amazing. It is an absolute explosion of satisfyingly beefy flavour, and it is seasoned with just the right amount of salt. It is perfect 👍🏻🍔. •
